  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help Dom escape the Mirror Dimension!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a terrible accident in a physics seminar, Dom wakes up in a weird dimension and meets a odd, friendly spirit who aids Dom throughout his mission to find the other students and the professor who bought them into this mess, and hopefully go back into the real world safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, throw and roll your way into a unique set of levels, each with their own reflection at the end that holds all kinds of surprises! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat levels in any order you want, at your own pace!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden collectibles that lead to hard and precise challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skill with more than 30+ Medals to collect</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way up the castle to unfold the truth of this very world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Figure out who the hell Miguel even is (seriously).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4457630/extras/12317b261f0922fe73904ca177fe1cb9.avif?t=1774129706\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help Dom escape the Mirror Dimension!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a terrible accident in a physics seminar, Dom wakes up in a weird dimension and meets a odd, friendly spirit who aids Dom throughout his mission to find the other students and the professor who bought them into this mess, and hopefully go back into the real world safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, throw and roll your way into a unique set of levels, each with their own reflection at the end that holds all kinds of surprises! </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat levels in any order you want, at your own pace!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find hidden collectibles that lead to hard and precise challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skill with more than 30+ Medals to collect</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way up the castle to unfold the truth of this very world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Figure out who the hell Miguel even is (seriously).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4457630/extras/12317b261f0922fe73904ca177fe1cb9.avif?t=1774129706\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p>",
